# SYLHN POS — Protection Manifest
#
# This file documents the protection system in place. DO NOT DELETE.
#
# Protection System Components:
# ============================================
#
# 1. scripts/protection-snapshot.js
#    - Creates a full backup of all source files to backups/snapshot-YYYY-MM-DD-HHMMSS/
#    - Generates a SHA-256 manifest at backups/manifest.json
#    - Run manually: `node scripts/protection-snapshot.js`
#    - Verify:       `node scripts/protection-snapshot.js --verify`
#    - Restore:      `node scripts/protection-snapshot.js --restore`
#
# 2. scripts/startup-guard.js
#    - Checks 70+ critical files exist before dev server starts
#    - Prints warnings if any are missing
#    - Fast (<100ms) — runs on every startup
#
# 3. scripts/keep-alive.sh
#    - Runs startup-guard.js before starting the dev server
#    - Auto-runs --verify and --restore if any files are missing
#    - Starts the dev server only after integrity is confirmed
#
# How the auto-restore works:
# ============================================
# When keep-alive.sh starts:
#   1. Runs startup-guard.js → checks 70+ critical files
#   2. Runs protection-snapshot.js --verify → checks all 133 files
#   3. If any are MISSING → auto-runs --restore → copies from latest backup
#   4. Only then starts the dev server
#
# What's protected (133 files):
# ============================================
# - src/app/** (page.tsx, layout.tsx, globals.css, all API routes)
# - src/components/** (all 30+ components including operations-dashboard)
# - src/lib/** (auth, security, validation, rate-limit, db, email, etc.)
# - src/hooks/** (all 6 hooks)
# - src/proxy.ts (middleware)
# - prisma/schema.prisma
# - public/ (manifest.json, sw.js, icons)
# - Config files (package.json, tsconfig.json, tailwind.config.ts, etc.)
#
# Backup location:
# ============================================
# /home/z/my-project/backups/
#   ├── manifest.json (latest — used by verify/restore)
#   └── snapshot-YYYY-MM-DD-HHMMSS/ (full file copies)
#
# To create a fresh snapshot after making changes:
#   node scripts/protection-snapshot.js
#
# To manually verify integrity:
#   node scripts/protection-snapshot.js --verify
#
# To manually restore missing files:
#   node scripts/protection-snapshot.js --restore
